    A text string that refers to a (Medication) Event. This is an Event from the UMLS semantic group of Chemicals and Drugs, pruned by RxNORM source. Based on generic Clinical Element Models (CEMs) Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015
